OL,3,CTwo men arrested following reports of
OL,4,Can assault in Barry
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested following
OL,7,Fan incident on Park Road in Barry.
OL,9,FAn 18-year-old man and 17-year-old boy
OL,10,Fboth have been arrested in the Roath
OL,11,Farea of Cardiff and remain in police
OL,12,Fcustody.
OL,14,FThe incident is said to have taken
OL,15,Fplace at around 10:30pm on Monday, 13
OL,16,FApril.
OL,18,FSouth Wales Police confirmed there
OL,19,Fwere reports that a person had been
OL,20,Fassaulted. However, no victims have
OL,21,Fcome forward or been identified.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
