OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776345056
OL,3,CTwo men arrested following reports of
OL,4,Can assault in Barry
OL,6,FEnquiries are on-going and checks have
OL,7,Fbeen made with the local hospitals.
OL,9,FA cordon remains in place between
OL,10,FPorth-Y-Castell and Porthkerry Park
OL,11,Fwhilst the investigation continues.
OL,13,FSeveral items were also recovered from
OL,14,Fthe scene for forensic examination.
OL,16,FIn a statement South Wales Police
OL,17,Fsaid: "please avoid the area and use
OL,18,Falternative routes where possible..."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
